  </p>
  <p>
   Distances -
   <span class="eq">
    <var>b</var>
    =
    <u class="input-7">3</u>
   </span>
   m,
   <span class="eq">
    <var>a</var>
    =
    <var>l</var>
    −
    <var>b</var>
    = 5 − 3 = 2
   </span>
   m
  </p>
  <p>
   <b>Internal forces</b>
  </p>
  <p>
   Bending -
   <span class="eq">
    <var>M</var>
    =
