     </span>
     2
    </span>
    <span class="b1">)</span>
    = 5 · 3 ·
    <span class="b1">(</span>
    2 +
    <span class="dvc">
     3
     <span class="dvl">
     </span>
     2
    </span>
    <span class="b1">)</span>
    = 52.5
   </span>
   kN·m
  </p>
  <p>
   Shear -
   <span class="eq">
    <var>V</var>
    =
    <var>q</var>
    ·
    <var>b</var>
    = 5 · 3 = 15
   </span>
   kN
  </p>
  <p>
   <b>Diagrams</b>
  </p>
  <p>
